# Kubernetes 1.29 + Docker + Calico (Operator) 集群部署指南

## 环境信息
- 操作系统：Ubuntu 22.04
- 容器运行时：Docker CE + cri-dockerd
- Pod 网络：Calico (Tigera Operator 方式)
- 节点规划：
  - Master：192.168.6.100 (主机名：master-node)
  - Worker：192.168.6.103 (主机名：worker-node)
- Kubernetes 版本：v1.29.0

---

## 一、基础环境准备（所有节点）

### 1. 设置主机名
```bash
# Master 节点
sudo hostnamectl set-hostname master-node

# Worker 节点
sudo hostnamectl set-hostname worker-node

2. 配置 hosts 文件
bash
sudo tee -a /etc/hosts <<EOF
192.168.6.100 master-node
192.168.6.103 worker-node
EOF
3. 关闭 Swap 并加载内核模块
bash
sudo swapoff -a
sudo sed -i '/ swap / s/^\(.*\)$/#\1/g' /etc/fstab

cat <<EOF | sudo tee /etc/modules-load.d/k8s.conf
overlay
br_netfilter
EOF

sudo modprobe overlay
sudo modprobe br_netfilter

cat <<EOF | sudo tee /etc/sysctl.d/k8s.conf
net.bridge.bridge-nf-call-iptables  = 1
net.bridge.bridge-nf-call-ip6tables = 1
net.ipv4.ip_forward                 = 1
EOF

sudo sysctl --system
4. 安装必要工具
bash
sudo apt update
sudo apt install -y ipset ipvsadm chrony
5. 配置时区与时间同步
bash
sudo timedatectl set-timezone Asia/Shanghai
sudo systemctl enable --now chrony
二、安装与配置 Docker（所有节点）
1. 安装 Docker CE
bash
sudo apt update
sudo apt install -y ca-certificates curl
sudo install -m 0755 -d /etc/apt/keyrings
sudo curl -fsSL https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu/gpg -o /etc/apt/keyrings/docker.asc
sudo chmod a+r /etc/apt/keyrings/docker.asc

echo "deb [arch=$(dpkg --print-architecture) signed-by=/etc/apt/keyrings/docker.asc] https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu $(. /etc/os-release && echo "$VERSION_CODENAME") stable" | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/docker.list > /dev/null

sudo apt update
sudo apt install -y docker-ce docker-ce-cli containerd.io
2. 配置 Docker（cgroup 驱动 + 镜像加速）
bash
sudo tee /etc/docker/daemon.json <<EOF
{
  "exec-opts": ["native.cgroupdriver=systemd"],
  "registry-mirrors": [
    "https://registry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com",
    "https://docker.mirrors.ustc.edu.cn"
  ],
  "log-driver": "json-file",
  "log-opts": {
    "max-size": "100m"
  },
  "storage-driver": "overlay2"
}
EOF

sudo systemctl daemon-reload
sudo systemctl restart docker
sudo systemctl enable docker
3. 将普通用户加入 docker 组
bash
sudo usermod -aG docker $USER
newgrp docker   # 或重新登录 SSH
三、安装 cri-dockerd（所有节点）
1. 下载并安装二进制文件
bash
VERSION="0.3.17"
wget https://github.com/Mirantis/cri-dockerd/releases/download/v${VERSION}/cri-dockerd-${VERSION}.amd64.tgz
tar -xvf cri-dockerd-${VERSION}.amd64.tgz
sudo mv cri-dockerd/cri-dockerd /usr/local/bin/
sudo chmod +x /usr/local/bin/cri-dockerd
2. 创建 systemd 服务文件
bash
sudo tee /etc/systemd/system/cri-dockerd.socket <<EOF
[Unit]
Description=CRI Docker Socket for the API
PartOf=cri-dockerd.service

[Socket]
ListenStream=/var/run/cri-dockerd.sock
SocketMode=0660
SocketUser=root
SocketGroup=docker

[Install]
WantedBy=sockets.target
EOF

sudo tee /etc/systemd/system/cri-dockerd.service <<EOF
[Unit]
Description=CRI Interface for Docker Application Container Engine
Documentation=https://docs.mirantis.com
After=network-online.target firewalld.service docker.service
Wants=network-online.target
Requires=cri-dockerd.socket

[Service]
Type=notify
ExecStart=/usr/local/bin/cri-dockerd --container-runtime-endpoint fd:// \\
  --network-plugin=cni \\
  --pod-infra-container-image=registry.aliyuncs.com/google_containers/pause:3.9
ExecReload=/bin/kill -s HUP \$MAINPID
TimeoutSec=0
RestartSec=2
Restart=always

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target
EOF

sudo systemctl daemon-reload
sudo systemctl enable --now cri-dockerd.socket cri-dockerd.service
四、安装 Kubernetes 1.29 组件（所有节点）
1. 添加 K8s 1.29 仓库
bash
sudo mkdir -p -m 755 /etc/apt/keyrings
curl -fsSL https://pkgs.k8s.io/core:/stable:/v1.29/deb/Release.key | sudo gpg --dearmor -o /etc/apt/keyrings/kubernetes-apt-keyring.gpg
echo 'deb [signed-by=/etc/apt/keyrings/kubernetes-apt-keyring.gpg] https://pkgs.k8s.io/core:/stable:/v1.29/deb/ /' | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/kubernetes.list
2. 安装并锁定版本
bash
sudo apt update
sudo apt install -y kubelet kubeadm kubectl kubernetes-cni cri-tools
sudo apt-mark hold kubelet kubeadm kubectl
3. 配置 kubelet cgroup 驱动
bash
sudo mkdir -p /etc/systemd/system/kubelet.service.d
sudo tee /etc/systemd/system/kubelet.service.d/11-cgroup-driver.conf <<EOF
[Service]
Environment="KUBELET_EXTRA_ARGS=--cgroup-driver=systemd"
EOF
sudo systemctl daemon-reload
五、初始化 Master 节点（仅在 master-node 执行）
1. 创建 kubeadm 配置文件 kubeadm-config.yaml
yaml
apiVersion: kubeadm.k8s.io/v1beta3
kind: InitConfiguration
localAPIEndpoint:
  advertiseAddress: 192.168.6.100
  bindPort: 6443
nodeRegistration:
  criSocket: unix:///var/run/cri-dockerd.sock
  name: master-node
  kubeletExtraArgs:
    cgroup-driver: "systemd"
---
apiVersion: kubeadm.k8s.io/v1beta3
kind: ClusterConfiguration
kubernetesVersion: 1.29.0
imageRepository: registry.aliyuncs.com/google_containers
networking:
  podSubnet: 10.244.0.0/16
  serviceSubnet: 10.96.0.0/12
2. 初始化集群
bash
sudo kubeadm init --config kubeadm-config.yaml
3. 配置 kubectl
bash
mkdir -p $HOME/.kube
sudo cp -i /etc/kubernetes/admin.conf $HOME/.kube/config
sudo chown $(id -u):$(id -g) $HOME/.kube/config
4. 记录 join 命令（输出末尾一行）
初始化成功后，屏幕会输出类似以下命令，请妥善保存：

bash
kubeadm join 192.168.6.100:6443 --token <token> --discovery-token-ca-cert-hash sha256:<hash>
六、加入 Worker 节点（仅在 worker-node 执行）
使用上一步保存的 join 命令，并必须添加 --cri-socket 参数：

bash
sudo kubeadm join 192.168.6.100:6443 --token <token> \
    --discovery-token-ca-cert-hash sha256:<hash> \
    --cri-socket unix:///var/run/cri-dockerd.sock
七、部署 Calico 网络（Operator 方式，Master 节点执行）
1. 安装 Tigera Operator
bash
kubectl create -f https://raw.githubusercontent.com/projectcalico/calico/v3.29.0/manifests/tigera-operator.yaml
2. 创建 Installation 资源 calico-installation.yaml
yaml
apiVersion: operator.tigera.io/v1
kind: Installation
metadata:
  name: default
spec:
  registry: quay.io/
  calicoNetwork:
    ipPools:
    - name: default-ipv4-ippool
      cidr: 10.244.0.0/16
      blockSize: 26
      encapsulation: VXLANCrossSubnet
      natOutgoing: Enabled
bash
kubectl create -f calico-installation.yaml
3. （可选）手动拉取镜像加速
若从 quay.io 拉取缓慢，可在所有节点执行：

bash
for img in node cni pod2daemon-flexvol kube-controllers typha; do
    docker pull quay.io/calico/$img:v3.29.0
done
4. 验证 Calico
bash
kubectl get pods -n calico-system -w
kubectl get nodes   # 等待所有节点状态变为 Ready
八、集群验证
bash
kubectl get nodes
kubectl run nginx-test --image=nginx
kubectl get pods -o wide
九、常见问题与解决
现象	原因	解决
Pod CrashLoopBackOff / Init:0/3	cgroup 驱动不一致	确保 Docker 和 kubelet 均使用 systemd
Failed to pull image "registry.k8s.io/pause"	默认仓库不可达	kubeadm init 时指定 --image-repository=registry.aliyuncs.com/google_containers
InvalidImageName	registry 字段格式错误	确保为 quay.io/（末尾有斜杠，无协议前缀）
磁盘空间满导致 Operator 异常	Docker 日志/镜像堆积	配置日志轮转，定期 docker system prune -a -f
crictl 连接报错	未指定正确的 runtime-endpoint	本环境使用 Docker，crictl 需指向 unix:///var/run/cri-dockerd.sock
十、日常运维建议
每天执行 kubectl get nodes 和 kubectl get pods -A | grep -v Running 快速巡检

每周执行 docker system prune -a -f 清理无用镜像释放空间

核心组件镜像建议在所有节点预先 docker pull 一次，防止后续重启时拉取失败
